message: Let's be fair, Bob. I propose a 60/40 split in my favor to start.  I'm feeling generous, but the clock is ticking.
I appreciate the gesture of generosity, Alice.  But I think a 55/45 split is more equitable, given the value of the money is going to decrease more for you with each passing round.
Bob, time is literally money for me in this game.  I'll meet you in the middle - 52/48.
